kquote><br />\n<br />\nChing你柒到喊喎<br />\n<br />\n乾電是直流電 (DC / Direct Current) : 電荷在一個電路中沿著單一方向流動。一般的電芯 (電池) ，不論體積大小或電壓，都叫乾電。 <br />\n濕電是交流電 (AC / Alternating Current) : 是指大小和方向都發生周期性變化的電流，因為週期電流在一個週期內的運行平均值為零，稱為交變電流或簡稱交流電。"},{"pid":"a65d755cb5e115362b52de0f61df6f65d4f58388","tid":355493,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"鴨記買隻 inverter, 電池要舊如汽車水電"},{"pid":"a383ac48285c5df58247df803119a378ef76f442","tid":355493,"uid":8461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"220V power inverter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df04df36cdf5937b4bc5add91eb1c16c07f2aef2","tid":355493,"uid":43015,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:15:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=At0advb9_fA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAt0advb9_fA&d=vJ%2Fr8w8JOc3Zr1%2BfMQSHpGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d626f34c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=At0advb9_fA</a>"},{"pid":"2cd98607e0e49c3707e09e6d3f8a60df301e23b0","tid":355493,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"inverter + DC source"},{"pid":"cc06d13fdd0d641bf6c248579e376c38e9143a7e","tid":355493,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"方法1: 12V大舊鉛/鋰電 + power inverter<br />\n方法2: 將檯燈裡面嘅電路拆走佢<br />\n內籠拆燈膽,貼滿12V白色燈條,焊個DC插座<br />\n同樣地,用12V大舊鉛/鋰電去俾電"},{"pid":"69818157d2a898643d0a453ec5661fea1b27f9ca","tid":355493,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T12:29:26.000Z","msg":"只要知個circuit 點行 做乜春都得<br />\n<br />\n電燈仔"},{"pid":"5d54a2caf4e8e0263170e040d7e380d953961146","tid":355493,"uid":16510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係買舊夠推盞燈既電<br />\n同inverter 插埋晒 就著得?<br />\n